data.description: Looking to grab a better interest rate? Well, HONEY THIS IS THE ONE! 4 beds, +Office, 3 car Garage includes shelter, Buttler style walk-in pantry, Laundry off the Owner's En-suite. 2 gas Fireplaces, Beautiful Views of the Greenbelt at the backyard and out the Expansive windows, Sprinkler system, French Drains. The Home Boast So many Beautiful and Luxurious details. We are so excited to share this beauty with you. The HOA includes a Park, Pool and Clubhouse. There are walking trails that will take you for a stroll around the farmer's cattle and a beautiful pond. People tell me they love living here so much, The Neighbors are great, the amenities are great, and the LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION is SPOT ON. We can't wait to meet you and show you your new home.
